{
  "title": "Citrusy Flaky Light Japanese Pistachio Crumble",
  "description": "This light and citrusy Japanese pistachio crumble is perfect for a quick snack or dessert, featuring a flaky crust with low-calorie-friendly bhuna spices.",
  "cuisine": "Japanese",
  "diet": [
